name: Graduation Event
invitation_text: Join us for a fun-filled day at the Summer Beach Party. Don't forget your sunscreen!
notes: Ensure there are enough beach umbrellas for shade.

name: Outdoor Party
invitation_text: Indulge in a delightful afternoon at the Spring Garden Tea Party. Hats and gloves are encouraged!
notes: Ensure the tables are decorated with fresh flowers and vintage tablecloths.

name: Music Concert
invitation_text: You're invited to the Halloween Haunt. Expect a night of spooky surprises and delicious treats!
notes: Make sure the fog machines and eerie lighting effects are in place.

name: Dinner Party
invitation_text: You are cordially invited to the Masquerade Ball. Dress code: Formal attire with masks.
notes: Make sure the stage is decorated with gold and silver accents.

name: Birthday Party
invitation_text: You are invited to this Birthday Party.
notes: Make sure there is not too many people.
